\n<\N[2]>That's strange, this one is in our language.
\fi"My castle is in ruins, I have suffered so these past few years."\fi
\fi"I have inscribed onto these tablets my thoughts and memories, though I do to have give credit to the tribesmen for the concept."\fi
\fi"The lands have been at peace for many years, however I feel a dark presence following me."\fi
